snippet.title: Citizen Sleeper 2: Starward Vector - Official Gameplay Reveal Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Get a first look at Citizen Sleeper 2 gameplay, a tabletop-inspired RPG, in a human and heartfelt sci-fi world.

Citizen Sleeper 2: Starward Vector is coming soon to Xbox and PC in early 2025.
